**Summary:**
This documentation describes Amplitude's Journeys chart feature (currently in beta), which combines legacy Journey, Pathfinder, and Pathfinder Users charts to analyze user conversion paths through product transitions, offering three visualization modes: Pathfinder, Journey Map, and Top User Paths with configurable conversion windows and event filtering.

